gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Timberwolves 113, Magic 92
gameRecap.excerpt: The Timberwolves defeat the Magic, 113-92.  Karl-Anthony Towns led the way with 28 points (5-5 3FG), six rebounds and five assists for the Timberwolves, while Rudy Gobert added 21 points and 12 rebounds in the victory.  Jalen Suggs tallied 20 points and five rebounds for the Magic in the losing effort.  The Timberwolves improve to 26-10 on the season, while the Magic fall to 21-16.
